#gggenomes也可以用genbank文件，本脚本就是提取整个基因组gbk文件中某个scaffold上的某段区域。
#本例子中，我们要截取Rhodotorula_araucariae_Y17376.gbk中scaffold_6上基因区段003019-003330 (序列区段187970-1043642)；
#因此，修改序列区段起始位点184558，即包含基因003018，这样剪切的结果从003019号基因开始，如果从187970作为序列起始位点，结果是从003020号基因开始。

#!/usr/bin/env python
from Bio import SeqIO
#index your gbk file as a dictionary
record_dict = SeqIO.index("/bigdata/stajichlab/xinzhanl/Comparative_genomes/final_genomes_gbk/Rhodotorula_araucariae_Y17376.gbk", "genbank")
#Check that it was indexed
print(record_dict)
#ID your chromosome of interest. This is the same as your contig ID
chrom1 = record_dict['scaffold_6']
#Find the specific start/stop you want to subset your gbk file. You can do this by ID'ing your gene start/stop for the region of interest using the gbk file.
chrom1_subseq = chrom1[184558:1043642]
#write the output to a new gbk
SeqIO.write(chrom1_subseq, "./R_araucariae_Y17376_scaffold_6_sub.gbk", "gb")
